                        Interchange</hi>. Version 3.6.0, 419‚Äì420. <ref target="https://www.tei-c.org/release/doc/tei-p5-doc/en/html/PH.html#PHSK">https://www.tei-c.org/release/doc/tei-p5-doc/en/html/PH.html#PHSK</ref>.</bibl>
               </listBibl>
            </div>
